016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThree people will not be shocked by terror, nor will they face the Reckoning, for they will be on a dune of musk until Allah finishes holding his servants accountable: a man who recites the Quran seeking\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17418,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/01\/believer-shaded-sadaqah\/","url_meta":{"origin":20663,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: Believers will be shaded by their charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 1, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, charity will extinguish the heat of the graves for their people. Only the believer can seek shade on the Day of Resurrection in the shade of his charity.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 3076 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26702,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/07\/05\/every-khateeb-confronted-khutbah\/","url_meta":{"origin":20663,"position":3},"title":"Sha\u2019bi on Khutbah: Every preacher is accountable on Judgment Day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 5, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Mubarak reported: Al-Sha\u2019bi, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cNo preacher delivers a sermon b